<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="../public/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>All-In Shipping & Fee Calculator</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>Media Mail Calculator</header>
    <content>

        <h1>Ship at the right price.
            <br> The first time!</h1>
         
         <p class="intro">Know how much a book is worth but don't know how much shipping costs are? How about Paypal Fees? Buying and selling books on non-traditional online market places, such as Reddit, can be very fulfilling.</p>

        <form action="/package" method="get" class="form-values flex">
            
            <input type="text" placeholder="Enter VALUE Here!" id="bookValue" name="bookValue" required minlength="1" maxlength="6" size="10" onsubmit="return false" >

            <input type="text" placeholder="Enter WEIGHT Here!" id="bookWeight" name="bookWeight" required minlength="1" maxlength="2" size="10" onsubmit="return false" >

            <button action="/submitPackage" class="submitWeight submitBook" method="'post" type="submit">Calculate!</button>
        
        </form>

        <div class="priceOne fade">
            <p>If you sell at <strong>$<span class="userValue">0.00</strong></span>, you will receive <strong>$<span class="userProfit">0.00</span></strong> AFTER shipping and Paypal G&S Fee.</p>
            <span>USPS Media Mail Fee: <strong>$<span class="shippingFee1">0.00</strong></span></span>
            <span>Paypal G&S Fee: <strong>$<span class="paypalFee1">0.00</strong></span></span>
        </div>

        <div class="priceTwo fade">
            <p>If you want to receive <strong>$<span class="userValue2">0.00</strong></span>, you will need to sell at <strong>$<span class="userSell">0.00</span></strong> which INCLUDES the shipping and Paypal G&S Fee.</p>
            <span>USPS Media Mail Fee: <strong>$<span class="shippingFee2">0.00</strong></span></span>
            <span>Paypal G&S Fee: <strong>$<span class="paypalFee2">0.00</strong></span></span>
        </div>

<ul>
<% for (let i = 0; i < package.length; i++) { %>
<li>
    <span><% package[i].weight %></span>
    <span><% package[i].rate %></span>
</li>
<% } %>
</ul>
    </content>
    <!-- <script src="../public/js/main.js" rel="script"></script> -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>